{"tid":472250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【一帶一路項目遇挫】巴基斯坦拒絕中方投資水壩項目","createTime":"2017-11-18T04:52:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T16:38:31.000Z","uid":39464,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c0a0f07dba7cc2cd248a84e72983ea1ba1726b70","tid":472250,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:52:16.000Z","msg":"巴基斯坦日報報道，水利水電開發署主席Muzammil Hussein表示，中國投資約一千億港元，以獲取迪阿莫巴沙大壩項目的所有權、運作和維護和安保權，他認為以上條件都是無法接受及違背巴方利益，所以拒絕中國對迪阿莫巴沙水壩提供的資金援助。<br />\n<br />\n該大壩位於印度河的克什米爾地區，距離跟印度主權爭議的地區相當接近。<br />\n<br />\n【環球網撤回批評巴方評論】<br />\n<br />\n消息傳出後，內地環球網曾發出評論文章，批評巴國媒體「刻意誇大炒作」，但不久就撤回文章。<br />\n<br />\n中國發起的一帶一路計劃，在巴基斯坦的投資佔比相當大，整個中巴經濟走廊計劃裡，中國承諾投資近四千億港元。<br />\n<br />\n較早前，尼泊爾亦突然宣布取消跟中國合作的興建水壩計劃。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2F&d=LokDDrC3299haMjCSi6EvG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=711d09f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/</a>"},{"pid":"499b0954659478722f23fc3e69a5c78b102b07b5","tid":472250,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T05:08:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa4520939126ff27b65556c1a32e29639cd41fe2","tid":472250,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T05:12:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl75